title: Jesús Cabeza
text: Jesús Cabeza (born 30 October 1959) is a Venezuelan <a href="boxing">boxer</a>. He competed in the <a href="Boxing%20at%20the%201980%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Middleweight">men's middleweight</a> event at the <a href="1980%20Summer%20Olympics">1980 Summer Olympics</a>.
